THE DUMB AS ROCKS HARDWARE LICENSE (DARHL)
===========================================================================

This device is so primitive and/or simplistic that its very existence is also its supplied source. 
By inspecting this device, you likely have ascertained all relevant facets of this device’s design to reproduce it as you wish.
Therefore, the creator has concluded it is futile to restrict the design.

As a result, the DARHL permits:
- Modification of the original design
- (Re)Distribution of the original design
- Sales or monitization of the device, both unmodified and modified

THE DARHL DOES NOT:
- Inherently grant rights to use existing trademarks, signatures, or supplicant artwork
- Inherently grant rights to distribute as or on behalf of the originating person, group, or organization
